#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "[[!meta robots=\"noindex\"]]\n"
msgstr "[[!meta robots=\"noindex\"]]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "<h1 id=\"verify-other\" class=\"step\">Verify that the other Tails is up-to-date</h1>\n"
msgstr "<h1 id=\"verify-other\" class=\"step\">Verifiqueu que l'altre Tails estigui actualitzat</h1>\n"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"To prevent\n"
"<span class=\"pc-clone mac-clone\">installing</span>\n"
"<span class=\"upgrade-clone\">upgrading to</span>\n"
"an outdated version of Tails with known security issues, make sure that the Tails you are\n"
"<span class=\"pc-clone mac-clone\">installing</span>\n"
"<span class=\"upgrade-clone\">upgrading</span>\n"
"from is up-to-date:\n"
msgstr ""
"Per prevenir\n"
"<span class=\"pc-clone mac-clone\">la instal·lació d'</span>\n"
"<span class=\"upgrade-clone\">l'actualització a</span>\n"
"una versió obsoleta de Tails amb problemes de seguretat coneguts, assegureu-vos que el Tails des del que esteu\n"
"<span class=\"pc-clone mac-clone\">instal·lant</span>\n"
"<span class=\"upgrade-clone\">actualitzant</span>\n"
"està actualitzat:\n"

#. type: Bullet: '1. '
msgid "Choose **Apps&nbsp;▸ Tails&nbsp;▸ About Tails**."
msgstr "Seleccioneu **Aplicacions</span>&nbsp;▸ Tails&nbsp;▸ Quant a Tails**."

#. type: Bullet: '1. '
msgid ""
"Verify that you are running **Tails [[!inline pages=\"inc/"
"stable_amd64_version\" raw=\"yes\" sort=\"age\"]]** released on [[!inline "
"pages=\"inc/stable_amd64_date\" raw=\"yes\" sort=\"age\"]]:"
msgstr ""
"Verifiqueu que esteu executant **Tails "
"[[!inline pages=\"inc/stable_amd64_version\" raw=\"yes\" sort=\"age\"]]** "
"publicat el "
"[[!inline pages=\"inc/stable_amd64_date\" raw=\"yes\" sort=\"age\"]]:"

#. type: Bullet: '   - '
msgid ""
"If you are running Tails [[!inline pages=\"inc/stable_amd64_version\" "
"raw=\"yes\" sort=\"age\"]], continue with the next step."
msgstr ""
"Si esteu executant Tails "
"[[!inline pages=\"inc/stable_amd64_version\" raw=\"yes\" sort=\"age\"]], "
"podeu continuar amb el pas següent."

#. type: Bullet: '   - '
msgid ""
"If you are not running Tails [[!inline pages=\"inc/stable_amd64_version\" "
"raw=\"yes\" sort=\"age\"]], click **Check for Upgrades**."
msgstr ""
"Si no esteu executant el Tails "
"[[!inline pages=\"inc/stable_amd64_version\" raw=\"yes\" sort=\"age\"]], feu "
"clic a **Comprova si hi ha actualitzacions**."

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "     Apply all upgrades as requested.\n"
msgstr "     Aplica totes les millores, com s'ha demanat.\n"

#, no-wrap
#~ msgid ""
#~ "   b. If you are not running [[!inline pages=\"inc/stable_amd64_version\" raw=\"yes\" sort=\"age\"]] then connect to the Internet\n"
#~ "   and to Tor. After a minute or two, *Tails Upgrader*\n"
#~ "   appears with instructions on how to upgrade. Apply all upgrades as requested.\n"
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "   b. Si no esteu executant [[!inline pages=\"inc/stable_amd64_version\" raw=\"yes\" sort=\"age\"]], connecteu-vos a Internet\n"
#~ "   i a Tor. Al cap d'un o dos minuts, *Tails Upgrader*\n"
#~ "   apareix amb instruccions sobre com actualitzar. Apliqueu totes les actualitzacions segons se us sol·liciti.\n"
